Turkish Parliamentary Candidate Found Dead, Anatolia Reports

-- B y   E m r e   P e k e r
-- 
2011-06-11T09:10:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-11/turkish-parliamentary-candidate-found-dead-anatolia-reports.html
A parliamentary candidate for
 Turkey ’s Democratic Left Party was found dead before tomorrow’s
election, two days after he disappeared, state-run Anatolia news
agency reported.  Bedri Aydin, 33, had been killed in a rural part of Bitlis
and rifle bullet shells were found close to the body yesterday,
the local prosecutor said, according to Anatolia yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emre Peker in Ankara at 
 epeker2@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden in Dubai at 
 barden@bloomberg.net . 